msgid "Suggestion: restore the missing file or replace this file URL with the current file URL."
msgstr "建议：恢复缺失文件，或将此文件 URL 替换为当前文件 URL。"

msgid "Suggestion: restore the missing media file or replace this image URL with the correct attachment URL."
msgstr "建议：恢复缺失媒体文件，或将此图片 URL 替换为正确的附件 URL。"

msgid "Suggestion: restore the missing resource or replace the URL in the source content."
msgstr "建议：恢复缺失资源，或替换源内容中的 URL。"

msgid "Suggestion: review the redirect target before replacing the source URL. External redirects may be intentional."
msgstr "建议：替换源 URL 前先检查重定向目标。外部重定向可能是有意设置的。"

